namic-access report in one prompt and asks it to cover the missing accesses in a single broad pass.\",\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1318:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:538:      \"optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration.md\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1319:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:552:    \"description\": \"Codex bulk dynamic-access strategy. Unlike the regular dynamic-access strategy, which iterates through uncovered classes and refines coverage class by class, this strategy gives the agent the full dynamic-access report in one prompt and asks it to cover the missing accesses in a single broad pass.\",\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1320:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:557:      \"optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration.md\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1321:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:571:    \"description\": \"Pi graphify-assisted bulk dynamic-access strategy. It first builds graphify context from downloaded source artifacts, then gives the agent the full dynamic-access report in one broad pass. Unlike the regular dynamic-access strategy, it does not run the class-by-class refinement loop.\",\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1322:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:5