:      \"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1335:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:759:    \"description\": \"Library-update strategy: skips primary workflow, directly runs dynamic-access coverage improvement on existing tests.\",\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1336:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:764:      \"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\",\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1337:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:779:    \"description\": \"Library-update bulk dynamic-access strategy: runs only the optimistic full-report workflow against existing tests, without per-class refinement.\",\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1338:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:784:      \"optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration-update.md\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1339:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:799:    \"description\": \"Library-update composite strategy: bulk dynamic-access coverage in one broad pass first, then per-class iterative refinement of any stragglers. Mirrors the iterative library-update strategy but starts with a faster bulk pass.\",\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1340:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:805:      \"optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration-update.md\",\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1341:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:806:      \"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1342:  forge/git_scripts/common_git.py:762:    \"\"\"Return fully covered dynamic-access categories that became uncovered.\"\"\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1343:  forge/git_scripts/common_git.py:795:    \"\"\"Fail PR publication if old/new stats show a dynamic-access category regression.\"\"\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1344:  forge/git_scripts/common_git.py:814:    \"\"\"Format a single dynamic-access stats entry.\"\"\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1345:  forge/git_scripts/common_git.py:823:    \"\"\"Return True when stats has the expected dynamic-access entry shape.\"\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1348:  forge/forge_metadata.py:3024:    \"\"\"Load dynamic-access coverage from the stored run metrics stats block.\"\"\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1349:  forge/forge_metadata.py:3054:    \"\"\"Resolve the dynamic-access coverage report path for a new-library issue.\"\"\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1350:  forge/forge_metadata.py:3060:        \"dynamic-access\",\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1351:  forge/forge_metadata.py:3061:        \"dynamic-access-coverage.json\",\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1352:  forge/forge_metadata.py:3066:    \"\"\"Load dynamic-access coverage directly from the generated report as a fallback.\"\"\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1353:  forge/forge_metadata.py:3196:        \"Analyze the generated tests, metadata, stats, and dynamic-access report in this repository. \"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1354:  forge/forge_metadata.py:3200:        \"- Explain briefly why dynamic-access coverage is missing or still very low.\\n\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1355:  forge/forge_metadata.py:3219:        f\"Automation completed for `{claimed_issue.issue_coordinates}`, but dynamic-access coverage remains \"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1356:  forge/forge_metadata.py:3221:        \"This suggests the generated tests are not exercising the required dynamic-access paths well enough.\\n\\n\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1357:  forge/forge_metadata.py:3223:        \"- Inspect the generated tests and compare them with the dynamic-access report to find uncovered call sites.\\n\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1358:  forge/forge_metadata.py:4010:    \"\"\"Append issue context and concrete chunk limits for oversized dynamic-access runs.\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1359:  forge/forge_metadata.py:4015:    (§WF-dynamic-access-exhaust-report).\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1360:  forge/forge_metadata.py:4049:            pipeline_argv.append(\"--keep-tests-without-dynamic-access\")\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1361:  forge/forge_metadata.py:4834:    (§WF-dynamic-access-exhaust-report).\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1362:  forge/forge_metadata.py:5090:    (§WF-chunked-dynamic-access-pr-linking, §GIT-issue-linking).\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1363:  forge/forge_metadata.py:6739:        \"--keep-tests-without-dynamic-access\",\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1364:  forge/forge_metadata.py:6742:            \"Forwarded to the new-library pipeline. Keeps generated tests for dynamic-access \"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1365:  forge/forge_metadata.py:6743:            \"strategies even when no dynamic-access coverage is added.\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1366:  forge/git_scripts/make_pr_improve_coverage.py:141:This PR improves dynamic-access coverage for {coordinates} by generating additional tests.\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1367:  forge/DEVELOPING.md:95:- Script results are written in `output/results.json` (§WF-dynamic-access-workflow, §WF-forge-workflow-drivers).\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1368:  forge/DEVELOPING.md:101:  [--keep-tests-without-dynamic-access] \\\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1369:  forge/DEVELOPING.md:126:- `--keep-tests-without-dynamic-access` keeps generated tests for dynamic-access workflows even if no dynamic-access call sites are covered.\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1370:  forge/DEVELOPING.md:386:coordinates, active dynamic-access classes, source-context paths, and Gradle\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1371:  forge/DEVELOPING.md:421:The `dynamic_access_iterative` workflow improves metadata accuracy by using the `generateDynamicAccessCoverageReport` Gradle task to identify which dynamic-access call sites (reflection, JNI, resources, serialization) are not yet covered by the generated tests. Instead of generating tests blindly, the workflow iterates class-by-class, sending the agent targeted prompts with the exact uncovered call sites for each class. After each attempt, the report is regenerated and coverage deltas are computed to decide whether to retry the same class or move on.\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1372:  forge/DEVELOPING.md:452:Composite strategies (run a primary workflow, then refine dynamic-access coverage):\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1373:  forge/DEVELOPING.md:459:#### Running a dynamic-access strategy\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1374:  forge/DEVELOPING.md:482:see `docs/workflows/dynamic-access.md`.\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1375:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:62:      \"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1376:  forge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:81:      \"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\"\n../1504-01be332b/human-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcutil-jdk18on:1.77/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T20-51-47-597822Z.log:1377:  forge/st